The,Polysync,Shared,Memory,REST,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Polysync,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,The,main,API,method,is,providing,an,interface,for,reading,and,writing,data,from,a,shared,memory,queue,Polysync,provides,a,platform,and,features,that,allow,for,creating,testing,and,deploying,applications,for,driverless,vehicles